DiveAnalyser - Class in analytics
This class has all the functionality to split a dive into its component divelets, extract these divelets and finally compute a number of features that represent the dive for interpretation and reporting.

DiveFeatures - Class in analytics
This class stores all the features extracted by DiveAnalyser and DiveInterpreter.

This class uses the PADITable and dive features computed by DiveAnalyser to interpret a dive.
